  "description": "<i>Battle for the Isle II</i> is a turn-base tactical strategy game, similar to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Panzer+General\">Panzer General</a> or <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=V+for+Victory\">V for Victory</a>. The player may select one side of the conflict: North Army Ataric or South Army Spectrumc. First army is located on the North-West, the second one on the South-West part of the island. Units are represented by tokens. The goal requires destroying all enemy troops. The unit can move or attack an opponent. The fire range is up to 5 fields.<br><br>\n",
